# Quick Start

Just go to cloned repo directory and follow the instructions.

Set correct network settings in VirtualBox and in Vagrantfile

    $ VBoxManage list hostonlyifs
    Name:            vboxnet1
    GUID:            786f6276-656e-4174-8000-0a0027000001
    DHCP:            Disabled
    IPAddress:       192.168.33.1
    NetworkMask:     255.255.255.0
    IPV6Address:     fe80:0000:0000:0000:0800:27ff:fe00:0001
    IPV6NetworkMaskPrefixLength: 64
    HardwareAddress: 0a:00:27:00:00:01
    MediumType:      Ethernet
    Status:          Up
    VBoxNetworkName: HostInterfaceNetworking-vboxnet1

    $ head -n5 Vagrantfile
    # -*- mode: ruby -*-

    intnetname="devnet"
    intdomain=".realloc.spb.ru"
    vbnet="192.168.33"

Populate cookbooks

    $ rake
    $ vagrant up rainbowdash

When you have VM configured, scp misc/solo.rb to vm:/etc/chef/solo.rb
and run
    $ chef-solo

# Building vagrant baseboxes

    $ rake baseboxes
    $ vagrant box add 'debian7x64' 'boxes/debian7x64.box'
